""" Image - rotate - rgb """
image = Image('files/1_100.jpg', 1, config=['resize=(64,64)'])
rotated = image.rotate(90)
self.assertTrue(rotated.shape, (64, 64))
rotated = image.rotate(180)
self.assertTrue(rotated.shape, (64, 64))
rotated = image.rotate(270)
self.assertTrue(rotated.shape, (64, 64))
os.remove('1_100.h5')
